## HOW OUTREACH IS DELIVERED (HubSpot AI fields)

Outreach sends from HubSpot sequences in the cloud, not from a laptop.

1. `osi-prospect-qualification` qualifies and writes the strategy note + a LinkedIn task.
2. `osi-outreach-sequence` drafts 6 emails and writes them to the contact's HubSpot AI fields (`ai_email_subject_1` to `_6`, `ai_email_body_1` to `_6`). The emails are written to HubSpot only, never printed in the chat. The confirmation line includes the LinkedIn URL and a clickable HubSpot contact link.
3. The LinkedIn task on Day 1 is the cue. When it comes due, enroll the contact in your HubSpot sequence (which references those AI fields as tokens). HubSpot sends.

One time HubSpot setup is required: create the 12 AI custom properties and a 6 step token based sequence. See SETUP Step 3.

