## THE SKILLS

- `osi-prospect-qualification`: core qualifier. Profile Mode (paste a URL), Company Mode ("find me prospects at X"), Auto Mode ("sweep my accounts"), Task Mode ("process my enroll tasks", picks up "Enroll in sequence" and "3 email sequence" to do tasks).
- `osi-outreach-sequence`: drafts the 6 email cadence and writes the AI fields. Called on a Yes.
- `osi-3email-new`: shorter 3 email cadence.
- `osi-3email-reengagement`: 3 email second touch for prior sequence recipients.
- `osi-old-customer-reengagement`: 5 email revival for dormant customers.
- `osi-cold-reengagement`: cold first degree LinkedIn connections, InMail tasks.
- `osi-job-change-prospecting`: weekly Sales Nav job change and new connection scan.
- `osi-email-task-drafts`: drafts replies for HubSpot email tasks due today.

Legacy (`skills/legacy/`, only for draining an old queue): `osi-email-sender`, `osi-monitor`, `osi-email2-rewriter`.

